ygData.subject: Re: Executioners Axe *spoiler*
ygData.msgSnippet: No you don t get the axe.  You just get to watch the Executioner kill the Innkeeper.  From what I have seen on the EQ Lizer, the axe comes from Lower Guk.
ygData.messageBody:
No you don't get the axe. You just get to watch the
Executioner kill the Innkeeper. From what I have seen
on the EQ Lizer, the axe comes from Lower Guk.

> > Gnasher Furrgut (I think thats his last name) is a named gnoll

> > completed, you get to watch the Executioner (a barbarian woman
> > in full platemail with the horned helmet) open a can of whoop-ass

> > hit when he died but since she killed him, no faction hit.
